- [x] Component-driven row rendering with `ComponentGrid` (2026-06-09)
- [x] `DesignedCardWrapper` added for card-level style composition (2026-06-11)
- [x] `ComponentGroupEditor` refactored with tab UI (layout/styles) and `CardDesigner` integration (2026-06-11)
- [x] `ComponentRenderer` extended with `MediaScraperCard` compound component (2026-06-11)
- [x] CSS sanitization added to `DesignedCardWrapper` for safe `customCss` rendering (2026-06-11)

### Next Steps
